---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Our Costs"
  description="Transparent information about Windeatts Solicitors' legal fees and costs. We believe in clear, upfront pricing."
  subtitle="We believe in transparency. Here's what you can expect."
  breadcrumbs={[{ label: 'Our Costs' }]}
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl">
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-(family-name:--font-heading) prose-headings:text-navy mb-12">
      <p>
        We understand that legal costs are a concern for many people. We are committed to being open
        and transparent about our fees from the outset, so you can make informed decisions about
        your legal matters.
      </p>
      <p>
        At your initial meeting or conversation, we will provide you with a clear estimate of costs
        and explain how our fees are calculated. We will keep you updated if anything changes during
        the course of your matter.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-(family-name:--font-heading) text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">How We Charge</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-(family-name:--font-heading) font-semibold text-navy text-lg mb-3">Hourly Rate</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          For many matters, we charge based on the time spent. Our hourly rates depend on the
          experience of the solicitor handling your case. We will always provide an estimate of
          the likely total cost at the outset.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-(family-name:--font-heading) font-semibold text-navy text-lg mb-3">Fixed Fee</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          For certain types of work — such as straightforward conveyancing, simple wills and
          uncontested probate — we can offer a fixed fee so you know exactly what you'll pay
          from the start.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-(family-name:--font-heading) font-semibold text-navy text-lg mb-3">Conditional Fee</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          For personal injury and some clinical negligence claims, we may be able to offer a
          "no win, no fee" arrangement. We will discuss whether this is appropriate for your case.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-(family-name:--font-heading) font-semibold text-navy text-lg mb-3">Legal Aid</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          Legal aid is available for certain types of work. We can advise whether you may be
          eligible and help you through the application process.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-(family-name:--font-heading) text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Indicative Costs</h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b-2 border-navy">
            <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-navy">Service</th>
            <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-navy">Typical Range</th>
            <th class="text-left py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Basis</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700">Residential conveyancing (sale or purchase)</td>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">&pound;850 &ndash; &pound;2,500 + VAT</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-gray-500">Fixed fee + disbursements</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700">Remortgage</td>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">&pound;500 &ndash; &pound;1,000 + VAT</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-gray-500">Fixed fee + disbursements</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700">Simple will (single)</td>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">&pound;250 &ndash; &pound;400 + VAT</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-gray-500">Fixed fee</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700">Mirror wills (couple)</td>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">&pound;400 &ndash; &pound;650 + VAT</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-gray-500">Fixed fee</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700">Lasting Power of Attorney (each)</td>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">&pound;350 &ndash; &pound;550 + VAT</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-gray-500">Fixed fee + registration fee</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700">Probate (uncontested, no IHT)</td>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">&pound;2,000 &ndash; &pound;5,000 + VAT</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-gray-500">Fixed or hourly</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700">Employment tribunal claim</td>
            <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">From &pound;3,000 + VAT</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-gray-500">Hourly rate</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-navy/5 rounded-xl p-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
      <p class="font-medium text-navy mb-2">Please note</p>
      <p>
        The costs shown above are indicative only and will vary depending on the complexity of your
        matter. Additional disbursements (third-party costs such as search fees, Land Registry fees,
        court fees and counsel's fees) may also apply. We will always provide you with a detailed
        estimate before commencing work.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        VAT is charged at the prevailing rate (currently 20%) on all fees and most disbursements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
